ScreensharingAgent(8)       System Manager's Manual      ScreensharingAgent(8)

NAME
     ScreensharingAgent – communicates with screensharingd to provide access
     to a user session.

DESCRIPTION
     The ScreensharingAgent command should not be run directly. Enable Screen
     Sharing or Remote Management to use this service.

